sequenceDiagram
actor Kasztelan
participant Browser
participant View as ApplicationView
participant Template as ApplicationTemplate
participant DB as Database

%% =========================
%% CREATE APPLICATION
%% =========================
Kasztelan ->> Browser: Open "Nowy wniosek"
Browser ->> View: GET /wnioski/new/

View ->> Template: load_default_template()
Template -->> View: base template (PDF/structured form)

View -->> Browser: render form template
Browser -->> Kasztelan: display form

%% =========================
%% FILL DATA
%% =========================
Kasztelan ->> Browser: Fill form data
Browser ->> View: POST /wnioski/create

View ->> Template: fillTemplate(user_data)
Template ->> Template: merge data into template structure

Template -->> View: filled application document

%% =========================
%% SAVE
%% =========================
View ->> DB: save ApplicationDocument
DB -->> View: confirmation

View -->> Browser: success response
Browser -->> Kasztelan: application saved
